    <item>
      <title>泰国推出 140 亿美元刺激计划以促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/thailand-gets-to-work-on-14-billion-cash-stimulus-to-aid-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国开始为数百万受益人签署现金发放计划，总理斯雷塔·塔维辛希望借此重振东南亚第二大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/thailand-gets-to-work-on-14-billion-cash-stimulus-to-aid-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:09:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言削减社会保障税以吸引老年人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普承诺取消老年人社会保障税，此举将减少部分美国老年人的税费，但会进一步给尚未退休人士的福利造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/trump-vows-to-cut-taxes-on-social-security-in-bid-to-woo-seniors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南港袭击事件后，英国各地爆发抗议活动，伦敦逾百人被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-01/over-100-arrests-in-london-as-unrest-breaks-out-across-uk-after-southport-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南港持刀伤人事件发生后，全国各地爆发进一步抗议活动，伦敦有 100 多人被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-01/over-100-arrests-in-london-as-unrest-breaks-out-across-uk-after-southport-attack</guid>
